{"tid":1798052,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"“講唔講港獨”係五毛好辛苦鋪咗幾日既日既分化風，千奇唔好入黎叫佢地番屋企再諗過計","createTime":"2019-12-26T02:36:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T09:35:08.000Z","uid":63045,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"197571e550ff49e0bf1dbad4424e225a5e22bf6c","tid":1798052,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T02:36:09.000Z","msg":"我今朝見到依個po上咗熱門，一睇啲口吻完全係分化引戰，起一起佢底<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />十足十五毛，屌依個屌個個<br />\npost link:<br />\n咪再提港獨<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1797961\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1797961</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我想講，過咗六個月大家應該睇得好清楚，無論你係主張大中華，港獨，自治，五大訴求，清算黑警，法輪功；共產黨都係唔會理你，從來都係唔係你死就係我亡既關係。其實諗深一層，共產黨滅亡先係香港人既最大公因數，共產黨唔滅亡以上無一個主張可以成立，至於支持邊個主張等佢滅亡咗先慢慢嘈啦，自己鐘意嗌乜咪乜，認同一齊嗌，唔認同就嗌其他，就係咁簡單，既然我地目標一致咁就無分化既理由，更加要團結一致。運動行到咁耐我地一路都係靠齊心同團結，不分化不割席，各位繼續努力。<br />\n<br />\n黎啦香港人，一齊發揮創意，第一屆傷害共產黨橋王大賽正式開始！！！！<br />\n<br />\n順便宣傳一下，一齊幫手加速支爆，IT /文宣手足睇下有冇計推比多啲人知：<br />\n發動第一次全港罷買中國貨！殲滅紅色經濟圈<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1789537\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1789537</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c8873f3e9e9814e4c1a8faedcc8f07c5fc540a61","tid":1798052,"uid":63045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T02:36:39.000Z","msg":"五毛番屋企再諗過啦"},{"pid":"57a515a6aeeddf5d39feea971b02c94ff9929d5a","tid":1798052,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T02:36:55.000Z","msg":"五毛番屋企再諗過啦"},{"pid":"0319ac5bfdf722374b418624e1bca00be30a8e8a","tid":1798052,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T02:37:05.000Z","msg":"五毛番屋企再諗過啦"},{"pid":"1a7c31352df7710750e5e72f11ca4c397e6e3600","tid":1798052,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T02:37:35.000Z","msg":"五毛番屋企再諗過啦"},{"pid":"589c82c14938dd1b00d88b29016489fab4d3eb96","tid":1798052,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T02:38:10.000Z","msg":"五毛番屋企再諗過啦"},{"pid":"e8c5476bc9bfdb77f0839cf3da0abac0f6a18465","tid":1798052,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T02:41:06.000Z","msg":"五毛番屋企再諗過啦"},{"pid":"b4234fbdb626c0aad8180da0f39d5063507b8146","tid":1798052,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T02:41:17.000Z","msg":"五毛番屋企再諗過啦"},{"pid":"860d2b5694bd3225058f73fe306da2f9f5d730ed","tid":1798052,"uid":319824,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T03:27:43.000Z","msg":"但依家係 搞獨立比其他人質疑 幫我哋口嘅人 例如政客<br />\n都駁唔到口喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家都知最終目的係搞獨立啦<br />\n但會唔會五大訴求到手左 有雙普選啦 <br />\n再先進一步講獨立<br />\n而唔係一野跨過左呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 理性討論"},{"pid":"5ba0251b78f1b57ea7e1fc3660540c6bc8b08b0f","tid":1798052,"uid":53870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T06:44:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8953efb8a14100b94348681d5c432e6aa3e88dff","tid":1798052,"uid":167548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5ba0251b78f1b57ea7e1fc3660540c6bc8b08b0f","tid":1798052,"uid":53870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T06:44:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T06:45:05.000Z","msg":"【和解文】如果你明白自己面對咩野，呢刻叫唔叫獨立有咩所謂。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1798283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1798283</a>"},{"pid":"8a2d0232cc741220858ef47c45cc104d0b6e7f1f","tid":1798052,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-1